items.headline: Welcome to the So You Think You Can Dance Wikia
items.desc: The XXX So You Think You Can Dance is a community site dedicated to the dance competition series So You Think You Can Dance. If you are a fan of this series, or even if you're just curious about it, then this is the place for you! Come explore our content and help us expand this database... or join us in discussion about the contestants, the dance genres & styles, or the series in general. All are welcome!
